With an optional 3mm insole, the Hana truly lets you Feel The World®."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vegan-friendly materials — the Hana’s upper is hemp canvas, the lining and external accents are microfiber. It washes easily with soap and water."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Huarache-inspired design — the heel/instep strap is not only eye-catching but functional."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flexible heel — feel free to step on the heel and wear the Hana as a slide"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Plus, Hana now has a new, “Rain-Friendly” upper."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"BTW, “Rain-Friendly” isn’t the same as “waterproof.” Fully water-proof shoes have a technical liner, sealed seams, and a "},{"type":"text","value":"much","bold":true},{"type":"text","value":" higher price. By pre-treating the Hana with a water-resistant coating, you get an extra layer of protection against light splashing right out of the box."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"As with all treatments of this type, it will wear off over time, so we recommend re-treating as you would other water sensitive footwear regularly depending on use."}]}]}
